title: YouTube Channel
body: Hey guys! Just trying to kick start my YouTube channel (www.youtube.com/nadnerb) . I've recently started doing league videos, but I play a lot if different games too, feel free to check it out, like and subscribe if you enjoy the content, just a reminder though I still haven't figured out all the kinks in the video recording and editing, so it's nothing exponential just yet, but hit me up with some ideas and constructive criticism!

replies.body: If you don't mind me asking, where did you get that intro? It's really sick. Great channel btw
